- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is another possible category as undecidability is a complexity result.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with infinite binary trees and their properties.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the least likely category as the paper does not involve any machine learning techniques or applications.
